<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>日出时分，暴风雨停了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼拉着王子游向海边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她把王子放到了白色的沙滩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在安全了。”她跟王子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，王子没醒过来，听不见她说的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼看着四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在海滩上，旁边有一个小花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花园里有白色长椅，周围环绕着柠檬和橙子树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看见花园后有一个高大的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好高的塔，好大的门啊！”小美人鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她扶着王子的头，手指拨开他湿湿的头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你醒醒吧，王子。”小美人鱼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，王子还是没醒过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你睡觉的时候，阳光会温暖你的。”她深情地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼看着他英俊的脸，亲了亲他的眼皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他甚至比我花园里的那个雕像还要帅。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，我的王子是真实的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，小美人鱼听见一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>塔发出巨大的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼抬头看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是教堂的铃声吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群少女从大门里走出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们穿着简洁的白裙，头发用白色的蝴蝶结扎了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她们是谁？在这里做什么？”小美人鱼很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>少女们围坐在长椅上，有说有笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不能让人类看见我！”小美人鱼害怕地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请多保重，我的王子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼离开了海滩，游向一块岩石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼为了不让人类发现，躲在海水泡沫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她看着海滩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”一个少女对朋友们喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然她穿着和别的少女一样的衣服，但她更漂亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她有一双绿色的大眼睛，睫毛又长又黑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑向海滩，看着那个年轻人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子还是一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来！我发现了一个人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>少女碰了碰他的脸，确认他还活着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，他醒了，对着她笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，梅丹，你发现了什么？”一个少女咯咯笑着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她们都跑向海滩，围在王子身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当王子看见围着他的美丽少女们时，他笑得更开心了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，他一直看着那个发现他的，被叫做梅丹的少女。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你救了我。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他应该谢谢我！”小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我救了他的命，他却不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去教堂暖暖吧。”梅丹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她领着他走过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别的少女跟在后面，走进了大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她们从我身边带走了我的王子。”小美人鱼在岩石后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她会哭，泪水会一滴一滴地落进大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，人鱼不会哭，所以没有眼泪掉进汹涌的波涛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要回到海底王国的家里去。”小美人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我会因为你回来的，我的王子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，她跳进了海里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>